.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-PEERS-SCORE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-peers-score \- show weighted health score for all peers
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-peers-score
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns a scored list of all peers based on connectivity, channel count,
and balance ratio. Also used as the backend for
.BR lightning-peer-score (1).
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{peer_id, score, connected, num_channels, balance_ratio}]
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-peer-score (1),
.BR lightning-peer-reputation (1)
